When that was happening,
right after that happened,

00:38:52.280 --> 00:38:54.890 align:middle line:84%
the government started
attacking the paper price.

00:38:54.890 --> 00:38:57.010 align:middle line:84%
It's been going on
now it's almost a year

00:38:57.010 --> 00:38:59.540 align:middle line:90%
like I've never seen before, OK.

00:38:59.540 --> 00:39:02.810 align:middle line:84%
Now, in the United States,
they've been so good at it,

00:39:02.810 --> 00:39:05.400 align:middle line:84%
