that they actually

00:39:05.400 --> 00:39:07.790 align:middle line:84%
have sapped sentiment
a bit this year.

00:39:07.790 --> 00:39:10.724 align:middle line:84%
Now I'd say my firm's
sales are about-- last year

00:39:10.724 --> 00:39:11.640 align:middle line:90%
they were record high.

